SUMMARY:Buffalo Bayou Park Wellness Walk
DTSTAMP:20260619T134035Z
DTSTART:20260701T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Buffalo Bayou Partnership on a free Wellness Walk led by L
	aura Conely\, founder of Urban Paths. Anyone and everyone is invited to wa
	lk through the paths of Buffalo Bayou while discussing topics including me
	ntal and physical health as well as the benefits of being exposed to natur
	e. \nEn Español\nEl primer miércoles de cada mes\, la traductora Marcella 
	Cabrera se unirá al grupo para ofrecer la caminata guiada en español. \nCo
	st\nFree \nDuration\n90 minutes / 3 miles \nMeeting Location \nAllen’s Lan
	ding Park (1005 Commerce St.) \nFREE REGISTRATION\n\nhttps://buffalobayou.
	org/event/2026-july-buffalo-bayou-park-wellness-walk-106/\n\nFrom Buffalo 
	Bayou Partnership
